import PyPDF2

pdf_path = '/workspace/benchmark/datasets/30-ERGO/ERGO/paper.pdf'
text = ''
with open(pdf_path, 'rb') as f:
    reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(f)
    for page in reader.pages:
        text += page.extract_text() + '\n'
print(text[:3000])
